SentenceNav is an NVDA add-on that allows you to read text by sentences, as opposed to by paragraphs or  words.

Please note that "Jump to nextÂ  paragraph with text" feature has been move to [TextNav](http://github.com/mltony/nvda-text-nav/) add-on that needs to be installed separately.

## Keystrokes
* Alt+Down arrow: Go to next sentence.
* Alt+Up arrow: Go to previous sentence.
* NVDA+Alt+S: Speak current sentence.
* Alt+Windows+Down arrow: Go to next phrase.
* Alt+Windows+Up arrow: Go to previous phrase.

